Package: HMSC
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical modelling of species community
Version: 0.7
Date: 2014-09-07
Author: F. Guillaume Blanchet
Maintainer: F. Guillaume Blanchet <guillaume.blanchet@math.mcmaster.ca>
Depends: MASS
Description: This package is design to analyse species community presence-absence data using hierarchical models. The package is based on the work of Ovaskainen and Soininen (2011) and Bhattacharya and Dunson (2011) and generalize some aspect of the developments made within what was proposed in the paper. For example, it can include species traits, multiple random effects and estimate co-occurrences 
License: GPL (>=2)
